611
00:29:28,940 --> 00:29:30,100
 pa sam radio i ja.

612
00:29:31,540 --> 00:29:32,740
 imaš onaj osjećaj,

613
00:29:32,740 --> 00:29:34,320
 mogu obratiti svakoga.

614
00:29:34,320 --> 00:29:36,360
 Samo ću mu reći koga Isus ljubi

615
00:29:36,360 --> 00:29:36,660
 i to je to.

616
00:29:36,660 --> 00:29:39,380
 I pročitaš neki redak iz svetog pisma

617
00:29:39,380 --> 00:29:39,700
 i čeka,

618
00:29:39,700 --> 00:29:40,600
 šta će biti?

619
00:29:40,600 --> 00:29:41,580
 Ko će se srušiti,

620
00:29:41,580 --> 00:29:42,420
 to će mu biti dobro,

621
00:29:42,420 --> 00:29:43,820
 ajmo svi u crkvi i tako,

622
00:29:43,820 --> 00:29:45,680
 ali to ne bi ba baš tako.

623
00:29:45,680 --> 00:29:46,980
 Pa molim evo ovim putem,

624
00:29:46,980 --> 00:29:47,500
 stvarno,

625
00:29:47,500 --> 00:29:48,700
 katoličku crkvu,

626
00:29:48,700 --> 00:29:50,260
 da otvori ured za obraćenike

627
00:29:50,260 --> 00:29:53,380
 i u tom uredu ono dođeš,

628
00:29:53,380 --> 00:29:54,260
 javiš se i on ti kaže

629
00:29:54,260 --> 00:29:55,300
 o šalter kod Mirijane,

630
00:29:55,300 --> 00:29:56,820
 tamo će te uzeti jedan papir,

631
00:29:56,820 --> 00:29:58,360
 staviti narukvicu

632
00:29:58,360 --> 00:29:59,200
 za svi nov obraćenik,

633
00:29:59,200 --> 00:30:00,380
 susre sa živim Bogom

634
00:30:00,380 --> 00:30:02,920
 i dati obrazat ponašanja

635
00:30:02,920 --> 00:30:04,180
 kako se ponašati u crkvi.

636
00:30:04,180 --> 00:30:07,080
 Jer imam osjećaj stvarno

637
00:30:07,080 --> 00:30:09,040
 da baš ti,

638
00:30:09,040 --> 00:30:09,620
 baš ti,

639
00:30:09,620 --> 00:30:10,260
 evo,

640
00:30:10,260 --> 00:30:11,940
 kod obraćenja

641
00:30:11,940 --> 00:30:13,140
 mi se nekako baš

642
00:30:13,140 --> 00:30:14,620
 ne ponašamo,

643
00:30:14,620 --> 00:30:16,340
 evo, ja se nisam ponašao kako treba.

644
00:30:16,340 --> 00:30:18,300
 Imaš osjećaj da može svakoga obratiti,

645
00:30:18,660 --> 00:30:20,440
 imaš osjećaj da drugi ne razumiju,

646
00:30:20,440 --> 00:30:21,180
 pa ovo je grešan,

647
00:30:21,180 --> 00:30:21,700
 pa ovo je ovo,

648
00:30:21,700 --> 00:30:22,300
 pa ovo je ovo,

649
00:30:22,300 --> 00:30:23,820
 pa sve bi trebalo biti idealno.

650
00:30:23,820 --> 00:30:26,020
 I tako i predlažem da prvo pravilo bude.

651
00:30:26,020 --> 00:30:26,760
 Evo, jedno prvo,

652
00:30:26,760 --> 00:30:28,260
 i ostalo neka radi crkva,

653
00:30:28,260 --> 00:30:28,500
 evo.

654
00:30:28,500 --> 00:30:30,200
 Neću se mi ješati.

655
00:30:30,200 --> 00:30:31,360
 Šalim se.

656
00:30:31,360 --> 00:30:32,920
 Evo, neka prvo pravilo bude

657
00:30:32,920 --> 00:30:35,800
 nađi nekog starijeg u vjeri,

658
00:30:35,800 --> 00:30:36,680
 iskusnijeg,

659
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:37,680
 stabilnijeg

660
00:30:37,680 --> 00:30:39,020
 i malo se savjetuj s njim.

661
00:30:39,020 --> 00:30:40,640
 Evo, to neka bude prvo pravilo.

662
00:30:40,640 --> 00:30:42,540
 Ja to nisam napravio.

663
00:30:42,540 --> 00:30:45,320
 Da, logično.

664
00:30:48,660 --> 00:30:51,360
 da bi me to spasilo puno tih nezralosti.

665
00:30:51,360 --> 00:30:53,220
 Evo, vidim ovdje u zajednici,

666
00:30:53,220 --> 00:30:54,980
 imate to neku duhovno pratiteljstvo

667
00:30:54,980 --> 00:30:55,980
 i to je stvarno predivno

668
00:30:55,980 --> 00:30:57,920
 i preporučam

669
00:30:57,920 --> 00:30:59,840
 u takvim pogotovo iskustvima.

670
00:30:59,840 --> 00:31:01,040
 I uglavnom,

671
00:31:01,040 --> 00:31:03,100
 evo, dok ja živim

672
00:31:03,100 --> 00:31:04,260
 taj obračenički zanos,

673
00:31:04,260 --> 00:31:06,600
 mene Džavao ne može

674
00:31:06,600 --> 00:31:08,440
 odvuć u grijeh.

675
00:31:08,440 --> 00:31:10,280
 Jer meni se tako grijeh gadi.

676
00:31:11,140 --> 00:31:12,900
 I on ide na ponovu taktiku.

677
00:31:12,900 --> 00:31:15,800
 A Džavaova taktika je bila

678
00:31:15,800 --> 00:31:17,980
 aktivizam.

679
00:31:17,980 --> 00:31:19,580
 Idem ga odvuć u aktivizam.

680
00:31:19,580 --> 00:31:21,880
 Jer prije negoli grijeh

681
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:24,140
 Džavao na mene preko aktivizma

682
00:31:24,140 --> 00:31:26,420
 me je odvukao na njegov teren.

683
00:31:26,420 --> 00:31:29,980
 Učlanio sam se u sve što može

684
00:31:29,980 --> 00:31:31,740
 doprinjeti boljitku, ne znam,

685
00:31:31,740 --> 00:31:32,840
 mjesta mog.

686
00:31:32,840 --> 00:31:34,900
 Znači svaka udruga sve organizirao,

687
00:31:34,900 --> 00:31:36,100
 maškare, gradio jaslice,

688
00:31:36,100 --> 00:31:38,380
 u crkvi sve, znači na sve strane.

689
00:31:39,320 --> 00:31:40,960
 I to je baš bila njegova taktika,

690
00:31:40,960 --> 00:31:42,360
 jer u tim trenutcima

691
00:31:42,360 --> 00:31:45,660
 ne tražimo ono što Bog želi za nas.

692
00:31:45,660 --> 00:31:46,720
 Nego ono, idemo, idemo,

693
00:31:46,720 --> 00:31:47,940
 sve je to dobro.

694
00:31:47,940 --> 00:31:48,580
 Što je dobro?

695
00:31:48,580 --> 00:31:49,980
 I Bogu je drago.

696
00:31:49,980 --> 00:31:54,000
 I tako mi sam uletio, eto, u sve

697
00:31:54,000 --> 00:31:56,540
 i Džavao gleda da bi mi odvojio,

698
00:31:56,540 --> 00:31:59,260
 da bi mi odvukao od osobnog odnosa s Bogom

699
00:31:59,260 --> 00:32:01,120
 kroz aktivizam.

700
00:32:01,120 --> 00:32:05,180
 I onda moj život spadne molitva na večer,

701
00:32:05,180 --> 00:32:08,440
 za vreme ručka, možda ujutru,

702
00:32:08,580 --> 00:32:10,600
 od se stave, stave, ovako.

703
00:32:10,600 --> 00:32:12,880
 I tako.

704
00:32:12,880 --> 00:32:14,660
 Ali ovaj, kako se zove,

705
00:32:14,660 --> 00:32:18,600
 tada uviđam da je taj osobni odnos s Bogom

706
00:32:18,600 --> 00:32:20,320
 možda najvažnija stvar.

707
00:32:20,320 --> 00:32:23,400
 Najvažnija stvar i kad vidim da mi to kopne,

708
00:32:23,400 --> 00:32:24,980
 baš mi onako bilo krive,

709
00:32:24,980 --> 00:32:26,760
 nekog sam poslijeo se stabiliziravati,

710
00:32:26,760 --> 00:32:27,440
 vraćati se,

711
00:32:27,440 --> 00:32:30,700
 znam da je najvažniji osobni odnos s Bogom.

712
00:32:31,240 --> 00:32:33,160
 Kada to fali, da je loše.

713
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:38,420
 I ja prestanem, prestanem malo u aktivizam,

714
00:32:38,420 --> 00:32:41,020
 prestanem to i prestanem drugima pričati o Bogu,

715
00:32:41,020 --> 00:32:42,580
 ali se bacimo ovaj dio,

716
00:32:42,580 --> 00:32:47,080
 di baš onako se družim s gospodinom.

717
00:32:47,760 --> 00:32:48,920
 Proodim vrijeme s njim,

718
00:32:48,920 --> 00:32:49,960
 razmatram.

719
00:32:49,960 --> 00:32:52,860
 Tako i u tom nekom osobnom odnosu s Bogom,

720
00:32:52,860 --> 00:32:54,960
 gdje sam više s njim,

721
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:57,140
 Bog mi je pokazao,

722
00:32:57,140 --> 00:32:58,980
 baš koz jednu situaciju u životu,

723
00:32:58,980 --> 00:33:01,800
 gdje me onako baš ponizio i dokazao mi da zapravo

724
00:33:01,800 --> 00:33:05,080
 ja ne trebam ništa pričat.

725
00:33:05,080 --> 00:33:08,180
 Nego, ako mi imamo osobni odnos s Bogom doba,

726
00:33:08,180 --> 00:33:11,620
 onda će naš svaki pokret biti evangelizacija.

727
00:33:12,400 --> 00:33:13,540
 Bog će nas sad iskoristiti,

728
00:33:13,540 --> 00:33:15,380
 a od ovog laprdanja, od toga nema ništa.

729
00:33:15,380 --> 00:33:18,680
 Odlazim na more, radit,

730
00:33:18,680 --> 00:33:22,160
 i sad između crkva se nalazi,

731
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:23,360
 meni između dva dućana.

732
00:33:23,360 --> 00:33:25,560
 Dućani su razmatili dosta,

733
00:33:25,560 --> 00:33:27,020
 ali crkva, moram tu proći pored crkve.

734
00:33:27,020 --> 00:33:30,480
 I ja sam tad u osobnom odnosu s Bogom dobar.

735
00:33:30,480 --> 00:33:33,800
 Ne pričam puno ljudima o Bogu,

736
00:33:33,800 --> 00:33:35,760
 nego nastoji živjeti kako treba.

737
00:33:35,760 --> 00:33:40,080
 I samo da kažem osobni odnos s Bogom,

738
00:33:40,080 --> 00:33:42,020
 ne smatram to odlazak u crkvu,

739
00:33:42,020 --> 00:33:42,880
 to se podrazumijeva,

740
00:33:42,880 --> 00:33:43,540
 nego ovo drugo.

741
00:33:43,540 --> 00:33:49,560
 I ja tada prolazim 20 puta u danu pored crkve.

742
00:33:49,560 --> 00:33:52,240
 I uvijek napravim jednu malu gestu,

743
00:33:52,240 --> 00:33:54,540
 napravim ovako znak križa,

744
00:33:54,540 --> 00:33:56,940
 ili odem u crkvu i poklonim se.

745
00:33:56,940 --> 00:33:58,940
 Evo, to je bilo što sam ja radio to ljeto.

746
00:33:58,940 --> 00:34:02,600
 I nikome nisam pričao Bogu.

747
00:34:02,600 --> 00:34:05,320
 Ali te moje neke male geste

748
00:34:05,320 --> 00:34:07,100
 vidio jedan mladić iz jednog kafića,

749
00:34:07,100 --> 00:34:11,020
 i to je njega nekako natjeralo da ode u crkvu.

750
00:34:11,640 --> 00:34:12,960
 Otiš on u crkvu,

751
00:34:12,960 --> 00:34:14,740
 normalno kako u tim malim mjestima

752
00:34:14,740 --> 00:34:16,920
 znaš koje sve bakici ide u crkvu,

753
00:34:16,920 --> 00:34:18,380
 kad se pojavi neko novi,

754
00:34:18,380 --> 00:34:19,920
 odmah ti je onako drago,

755
00:34:19,920 --> 00:34:21,600
 super, još je to bio neki mladić,

756
00:34:21,600 --> 00:34:24,060
 ja stvarno nisam mislio da ja imam veze s tim.

757
00:34:25,220 --> 00:34:27,740
 dok na kraj ljeta on dolazi do mene,

758
00:34:27,740 --> 00:34:30,220
 onako predstavio mi se i kaže,

759
00:34:30,220 --> 00:34:32,320
 evo samo da ti zahvalim,

760
00:34:32,320 --> 00:34:34,740
 radi onoga što si ti križom

761
00:34:34,740 --> 00:34:36,900
 križio ispred crkve,

762
00:34:36,900 --> 00:34:39,800
 ja sam otišao u crkvu,

763
00:34:40,320 --> 00:34:41,640
 i mene je buzila Božja ljubav

764
00:34:41,640 --> 00:34:45,380
 i ja sam razgovarao danas sa kapelanom i sa župnikom

765
00:34:45,380 --> 00:34:48,500
 i ja ću postati katolički svećenik,

766
00:34:48,500 --> 00:34:49,740
 idem u sjemenište.

767
00:34:50,820 --> 00:34:52,620
 Mene je to onako baš dotaklo

768
00:34:52,620 --> 00:34:55,960
 i on i je sad katolički svećenik

769
00:34:55,960 --> 00:34:57,120
 i sretno živi svoj poziv.

770
00:34:57,120 --> 00:35:01,240
 Tako, tada sam presto puno pričati o Bogu,

771
00:35:01,240 --> 00:35:05,520
 nego nastavimo živjeti u tom nekom osobnom ondosu s Bogom,

772
00:35:05,520 --> 00:35:07,520
 a onda će nas Bog iskoristiti

773
00:35:07,520 --> 00:35:09,520
 za sve što ono što nam treba,

774
00:35:09,520 --> 00:35:10,620
 sluge smo beskorisni.

775
00:35:10,620 --> 00:35:15,760
 Tada kad sam čuo od njega

776
00:35:15,760 --> 00:35:18,560
 da ide za svećenik i tako,

777
00:35:18,560 --> 00:35:20,460
 nakon toga normalno je bilo

778
00:35:20,460 --> 00:35:22,880
 da i ja razmišljam što je za mene,

779
00:35:22,880 --> 00:35:24,740
 što ću ja, koji je moj poziv.

780
00:35:24,740 --> 00:35:27,620
 Ali vrlo brzo meni Bog govori

781
00:35:27,620 --> 00:35:29,480
 da je to bračni život,

782
00:35:29,480 --> 00:35:30,920
 da je život sa ženom

783
00:35:30,920 --> 00:35:31,860
 i hvala Bogu,

784
00:35:31,860 --> 00:35:34,120
 mislim da je svećenik i poziv stvarno jako težak.

785
00:35:34,120 --> 00:35:38,500
 I tako da ja tada odlučim,

786
00:35:38,500 --> 00:35:40,280
 ok, to je bračni poziv, dobro,

787
00:35:40,280 --> 00:35:41,340
 ali ne znam šta s tim,

788
00:35:41,340 --> 00:35:43,580
 što, Bože,

789
00:35:43,580 --> 00:35:45,140
 i ja imam takav neki odnos s Bogom

790
00:35:45,140 --> 00:35:48,160
 da ja kažem, ok, da, treba bi se ženiti,

791
00:35:48,160 --> 00:35:49,560
 ali što, kako,

792
00:35:50,100 --> 00:35:51,720
 ne znam što napraviti, što,

793
00:35:51,720 --> 00:35:53,020
 evo, krenut ću moliti, pa šta.

794
00:35:53,020 --> 00:35:54,240
 I baš tako,

795
00:35:54,240 --> 00:35:55,580
 krenem moliti,

796
00:35:55,580 --> 00:35:56,880
 krenem moliti,

797
00:35:56,880 --> 00:35:59,160
 i Bog mi nekako govori

798
00:35:59,160 --> 00:36:00,200
 kroz vrijeme,

799
00:36:00,200 --> 00:36:01,500
 mi govori

800
00:36:01,500 --> 00:36:04,620
 kao korake,

801
00:36:04,620 --> 00:36:06,560
 kako se dobro ženiti.

802
00:36:07,560 --> 00:36:08,460
 ja te korake

803
00:36:08,460 --> 00:36:10,340
 slušam.

804
00:36:10,340 --> 00:36:11,640
 Sve ispoštujem

805
00:36:11,640 --> 00:36:12,860
 i sretno se ženim.

806
00:36:12,860 --> 00:36:13,600
 Ali,

807
00:36:13,600 --> 00:36:14,980
 ali,

808
00:36:14,980 --> 00:36:17,260
 sad ću ja te korake,

809
00:36:17,260 --> 00:36:21,180
 evo,

810
00:36:21,180 --> 00:36:22,660
 evo, kako je to dobro,

811
00:36:22,660 --> 00:36:23,720
 morat ću na pamet korake,

812
00:36:23,720 --> 00:36:25,420
 da sam papir izgubio od koraka,

813
00:36:25,420 --> 00:36:27,300
 ali dobro,

814
00:36:27,300 --> 00:36:28,640
 nema veze, znam ih na pamet,

815
00:36:28,640 --> 00:36:29,060
 pa ih,

816
00:36:29,120 --> 00:36:30,040
 da sam ja to prošao.

817
00:36:30,040 --> 00:36:30,880
 Evo,

818
00:36:30,880 --> 00:36:32,240
 evo, daj, mikrova.

819
00:36:32,240 --> 00:36:35,940
 Ok,

820
00:36:35,940 --> 00:36:39,340
 prva stvar koju mi je Bog stavio na srce,

821
00:36:39,340 --> 00:36:39,560
 evo,

822
00:36:39,560 --> 00:36:40,700
 ja vam govorim ovako,

823
00:36:40,700 --> 00:36:42,740
 čisto da neću vas tužit,

824
00:36:42,740 --> 00:36:43,720
 možete ovo i kopirat,

825
00:36:43,720 --> 00:36:44,380
 ali, evo,

826
00:36:44,380 --> 00:36:45,620
 slobodno uzmite ovo.

827
00:36:47,280 --> 00:36:49,600
 Prvi neki korak koji mi je Bog stavio na srce

828
00:36:49,600 --> 00:36:50,880
 i ja sam ga poslušao je to,

829
00:36:50,880 --> 00:36:52,060
 da molim za ženu.

830
00:36:52,060 --> 00:36:53,140
 I, stop,

831
00:36:53,140 --> 00:36:53,960
 to je kraj,

832
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:56,260
 ovaj, kraj nakane,

833
00:36:56,260 --> 00:36:57,340
 moliti za ženu.

834
00:36:57,340 --> 00:37:00,020
 Ali, moliti se majci Božjoj.

835
00:37:00,020 --> 00:37:01,240
 To je bio prvi korak.

836
00:37:01,240 --> 00:37:04,520
 Nekako majka zna što sino treba,

837
00:37:04,520 --> 00:37:06,500
 a i čeri.

838
00:37:06,500 --> 00:37:08,660
 Drugi korak,

839
00:37:08,660 --> 00:37:10,620
 jako važan korak,

840
00:37:10,620 --> 00:37:12,200
 na kojem je molitva

841
00:37:12,200 --> 00:37:14,400
 baš odvela do tog koraka,

842
00:37:14,400 --> 00:37:16,520
 a to je obrati pažnje na brakove oko sebe

843
00:37:16,520 --> 00:37:17,900
 i vidjet će što želiš.

844
00:37:17,900 --> 00:37:21,800
 Kada molite za ženu

845
00:37:21,800 --> 00:37:25,100
 i obratite pažnje na brakove oko sebe,

846
00:37:25,100 --> 00:37:27,380
 ja sam vrlo brzo vidio,

847
00:37:27,380 --> 00:37:30,480
 vrlo sam brzo vidio ono što ne želim.

848
00:37:30,480 --> 00:37:32,280
 To se nekako vrlo brzo pokaže.

849
00:37:32,280 --> 00:37:34,220
 Imamo tako puno primjera brakova.

850
00:37:34,220 --> 00:37:35,380
 Ali isto tako,

851
00:37:35,380 --> 00:37:39,040
 ima brakova oko nas koji su onako predivni

852
00:37:39,040 --> 00:37:41,920
 i tu će nam Bog pokazati što želim.

853
00:37:41,920 --> 00:37:43,700
 Tu mi je Bog pokazao što želim.

854
00:37:43,700 --> 00:37:46,260
 I kada sam vidio što želim,

855
00:37:46,260 --> 00:37:47,620
 u tim brakovima

856
00:37:47,620 --> 00:37:51,280
 i kako bih želio da mi žena bude,

857
00:37:51,280 --> 00:37:52,920
 paralelno,

858
00:37:52,920 --> 00:37:56,060
 sam vidio i kakav bi ja muškara

859
00:37:56,060 --> 00:37:56,880
 sreo postati.

860
00:37:56,880 --> 00:38:00,560
 Što je sve to u tim brakovima

861
00:38:00,560 --> 00:38:04,160
 i onda tu je jako lijepa ovaj sirah 636.

862
00:38:04,160 --> 00:38:06,840
 Kaže, ako vidiš razumna čovjeka,

863
00:38:06,840 --> 00:38:07,900
 rado ga posjeti

864
00:38:07,900 --> 00:38:08,880
 i neka ti stopalo

865
00:38:08,880 --> 00:38:11,560
 oteru njegov prag kuće.

866
00:38:11,560 --> 00:38:12,760
 To je onako dobro.

867
00:38:12,840 --> 00:38:14,020
 Kada vidite takav brak,

868
00:38:14,020 --> 00:38:17,280
 evo, ja sam nekog postao kao tajni agent.

869
00:38:18,020 --> 00:38:20,040
 dolazio bi tako špio u goste i to.

870
00:38:20,040 --> 00:38:23,440
 I gledao bi što mi se sviđa,

871
00:38:23,440 --> 00:38:25,200
 što mi se ne sviđa

872
00:38:25,200 --> 00:38:26,900
 i kakav bi ja trebao postati

873
00:38:26,900 --> 00:38:28,540
 i kakavu bi ženu trebao tražiti.

874
00:38:28,900 --> 00:38:30,140
 Jer tada u tim godinama

875
00:38:30,140 --> 00:38:33,540
 imamo filozofiju svakako o ženama

876
00:38:33,540 --> 00:38:35,020
 i kakvu mi ženu tražimo

877
00:38:35,020 --> 00:38:36,900
 i kakvom bi žena trebala biti

878
00:38:36,900 --> 00:38:37,500
 i šta to.

879
00:38:37,500 --> 00:38:39,000
 Ali kad obratimo pažnju

880
00:38:39,000 --> 00:38:40,040
 na brakove oko sebe,

881
00:38:40,040 --> 00:38:42,620
 vrlo brzo vidimo ono što nam se sviđa.

882
00:38:42,620 --> 00:38:44,720
 I vjerujte mi, svak od vas zna,

883
00:38:44,720 --> 00:38:46,200
 evo to znam na vlastite kože,

884
00:38:46,200 --> 00:38:46,820
 sam osjetio,

885
00:38:46,820 --> 00:38:48,540
 zna, odmah sam vidio,

886
00:38:48,540 --> 00:38:50,440
 da ja zapravo znam što želim.

887
00:38:51,120 --> 00:38:52,880
 kada sam pogledao tako brakove.

888
00:38:52,880 --> 00:38:54,280
 Ali prvo sam vidio što ne želim.

889
00:38:54,280 --> 00:38:58,780
 Treći korak na koji me je Bog tada odveo

890
00:38:58,780 --> 00:39:00,500
 je kad znaš što želiš,

891
00:39:00,500 --> 00:39:02,420
 moli precizno

892
00:39:02,420 --> 00:39:04,980
 i upiši muža i ženu kako bi htio.

893
00:39:04,980 --> 00:39:07,960
 Tada kada znam već što bi htio,

894
00:39:07,960 --> 00:39:09,620
 tada ste opasni igračevo,

895
00:39:09,620 --> 00:39:11,040
 tada sam ja postao opasan igrač,

896
00:39:11,040 --> 00:39:12,880
 znam što želim, molim,

897
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:15,060
 znam kakav bi želio postati,

898
00:39:15,060 --> 00:39:16,260
 znam kakvu ženu hoću

899
00:39:16,260 --> 00:39:17,480
 i tako molim precizno.

900
00:39:17,480 --> 00:39:19,340
 I najvažniji korak,

901
00:39:19,340 --> 00:39:20,140
 četvrti korak,

902
00:39:20,580 --> 00:39:22,400
 bez ova tri koraka ne znači ništa,

903
00:39:22,400 --> 00:39:23,400
 bez četvrto koraka,

904
00:39:23,400 --> 00:39:25,060
 a četvrti korak je pokreni se.

905
00:39:25,060 --> 00:39:28,260
 Da, ono, vjerojatno vam neće pokucati na prozor.

906
00:39:28,260 --> 00:39:29,880
 Jesi ti možda ti molio za mene?

907
00:39:29,880 --> 00:39:32,480
 To se neće dogoditi.

908
00:39:32,480 --> 00:39:35,160
 I s to poslu da vam odmah razbijem,

909
00:39:35,160 --> 00:39:36,640
 ono nije istina,

910
00:39:36,640 --> 00:39:38,460
 ono kad se sudare na čošku zgrade,

911
00:39:38,460 --> 00:39:39,860
 pa im ispadnu knjige iz ruku,

912
00:39:39,860 --> 00:39:40,700
 pa iskuplja i skupa,

913
00:39:40,700 --> 00:39:42,100
 pa se pogledaju, pa se zaljube.

914
00:39:42,100 --> 00:39:43,580
 To se isto neće desiti.

915
00:39:43,580 --> 00:39:45,820
 Nego baš ovo, pokreni se.

916
00:39:45,820 --> 00:39:48,880
 Tako sam ja bio u tom nekom četvrtom koraku

917
00:39:48,880 --> 00:39:50,240
 gdje sam se baš pokrenuo.

918
00:39:50,240 --> 00:39:53,200
 Pokrenuo sam se tako jako da mi je,

919
00:39:53,200 --> 00:39:56,300
 da sam, moj sam suprugu upoznao u autobusu

920
00:39:56,300 --> 00:39:58,580
 i, ono, upoznao sam se s njom,

921
00:39:58,580 --> 00:39:59,820
 sjeo, to iskoristio priliku,

922
00:39:59,820 --> 00:40:01,300
 ja krenuo nešto tako pričati.

923
00:40:01,300 --> 00:40:02,420
 Ona mi je zaspala.

924
00:40:04,060 --> 00:40:05,740
 Ali kako sam bio u ovom koraku,

925
00:40:05,740 --> 00:40:07,780
 pokreni se i znao što želim i znao,

926
00:40:07,780 --> 00:40:08,560
 nisam odustao.

927
00:40:08,560 --> 00:40:11,620
 Tako da, sretno sam oženjen,

928
00:40:11,620 --> 00:40:13,120
 evo, 2018. godine.

929
00:40:13,120 --> 00:40:16,840
 Dobio sam u braku petero djece,

930
00:40:16,840 --> 00:40:17,700
 ko što sam rekao,

931
00:40:17,700 --> 00:40:19,240
 Marija, 2019.

932
00:40:20,880 --> 00:40:21,880
 Josipa, 2021.

933
00:40:21,880 --> 00:40:23,820
 Estera, 2022.

934
00:40:23,820 --> 00:40:26,500
 Ljubica, 2023.

935
00:40:26,500 --> 00:40:28,360
 I David, sada mali,

936
00:40:28,360 --> 00:40:30,160
 evo, radi toga mi supruga nije mogla doći,

937
00:40:30,160 --> 00:40:31,080
 ja je pozdravljam.

938
00:40:31,080 --> 00:40:33,380
 David ima jedan mjesec,

939
00:40:33,380 --> 00:40:34,340
 2024.

940
00:40:34,340 --> 00:40:53,900
 Da, evo, pa bi progovorio,

941
00:40:53,900 --> 00:40:58,200
 možda u ovom dijelu bi progovorio

942
00:40:58,200 --> 00:41:02,780
 upravo o toj otvorenosti životu.

943
00:41:03,360 --> 00:41:06,140
 evo, nekako bi na to prešo

944
00:41:06,140 --> 00:41:09,680
 i rekao bi da je sada,

945
00:41:09,680 --> 00:41:11,680
 tako sam ja osjetio,

946
00:41:11,680 --> 00:41:13,680
 da je sada nekako živimo u vremenu

947
00:41:13,680 --> 00:41:15,660
 koji ne gleda baš blagonaklono

948
00:41:15,660 --> 00:41:19,300
 na obitelji sa puno djece.

949
00:41:19,300 --> 00:41:21,740
 I ja bi vam ispričao jednu priču

950
00:41:21,740 --> 00:41:23,480
 gdje sam osjetio da naš zapadna

951
00:41:23,480 --> 00:41:26,420
 civilizacija nekako ide u tom

952
00:41:26,420 --> 00:41:27,620
 potpuno krivom smjeru.

953
00:41:27,620 --> 00:41:30,620
 I ispričao vam događaj

954
00:41:30,620 --> 00:41:33,340
 koji sam baš osjetio na svoje kore.

955
00:41:33,340 --> 00:41:36,120
 doži, ja sam ovo ljeto bio u Neomu

956
00:41:36,120 --> 00:41:40,280
 i sada ja sa mojim, sa mojim, ono, četiri cure

957
00:41:40,280 --> 00:41:42,060
 idemo prema plaži.

958
00:41:42,060 --> 00:41:44,440
 Došli smo, došli smo, ovaj, tamo prvi dan

959
00:41:44,440 --> 00:41:46,040
 kod našeg prijatelja Milana,

960
00:41:46,040 --> 00:41:48,120
 pozdravljam ga ovim putem

961
00:41:48,120 --> 00:41:50,120
 i sada mi odlazimo, odlazimo na plažu,

962
00:41:50,120 --> 00:41:53,800
 pun ja rekvizita, pun svega,

963
00:41:54,300 --> 00:41:57,480
 ono, natrpam cijeli, idem sa ovim mojim curama

964
00:41:57,480 --> 00:41:59,320
 i moja supruga je trudna.

965
00:41:59,320 --> 00:42:02,060
 Dolazimo na plažu i tada,

966
00:42:02,060 --> 00:42:05,180
 tada kako se zove,

967
00:42:05,180 --> 00:42:06,920
 kako je to na plaži,

968
00:42:06,920 --> 00:42:08,200
 bi bivao uvijek opušteno,

969
00:42:08,200 --> 00:42:11,080
 prilazim meni neke starije gospođe,

970
00:42:11,080 --> 00:42:13,020
 uvijek imam problema s tim starijim gospođama,

971
00:42:13,020 --> 00:42:18,800
 meni i ženi i onako sa onim komentarima

972
00:42:18,800 --> 00:42:21,020
 koje ja jako često čujem,

973
00:42:21,020 --> 00:42:23,680
 ali je ova situacija baš bila onako posebna.

974
00:42:23,680 --> 00:42:25,380
 Oni dolazi kao,

975
00:42:25,380 --> 00:42:28,760
 a, super, i ovo kako su slatke,

976
00:42:28,760 --> 00:42:32,100
 kaže, o, majstore, bravo,

977
00:42:32,100 --> 00:42:33,760
 kao, lako tebi,

978
00:42:33,760 --> 00:42:36,300
 sad, ovo, žena, ispašta i tako dalje

979
00:42:36,300 --> 00:42:39,340
 i tako te neke, ovaj, zedljive komentare

980
00:42:39,340 --> 00:42:41,060
 i ja sad ne znam,

981
00:42:41,060 --> 00:42:43,420
 moću krenut na šalu, šta ću, kako ću, ovaj,

982
00:42:43,420 --> 00:42:45,420
 ništa, ja malo to ignoriram

983
00:42:45,420 --> 00:42:46,760
 i tako kreću tu i oni,

984
00:42:46,760 --> 00:42:48,600
 o, jadnice moja i tako,

985
00:42:48,600 --> 00:42:50,100
 suproko, ma što jadna, pa kako,

986
00:42:50,100 --> 00:42:52,660
 mi to uživamo na plaži, kupamo se i tako.

987
00:42:52,660 --> 00:42:55,220
 I u tom trenutku, deset metara od nas

988
00:42:55,220 --> 00:42:57,280
 stoji dvije muslimanske obitelji.

989
00:42:57,280 --> 00:42:59,780
 Hrpa djece, oni si igraju.

990
00:42:59,780 --> 00:43:01,240
 Oni vide to,

991
00:43:01,240 --> 00:43:03,420
 nas tu traje to, ti komentari traje.

992
00:43:03,420 --> 00:43:04,900
 Ja sam malo tu snima ovako,

993
00:43:04,900 --> 00:43:06,300
 provam krenut na šalu,

994
00:43:06,300 --> 00:43:07,880
 provam onda ozbiljno, vidim,

995
00:43:08,320 --> 00:43:09,840
 ne ide, morat ću promijeniti mjesto.

996
00:43:09,840 --> 00:43:11,460
 I

997
00:43:11,460 --> 00:43:14,180
 te muslimanske obitelji

998
00:43:14,180 --> 00:43:15,980
 prilaze, žene

999
00:43:15,980 --> 00:43:18,240
 od, žene dolaze kod moje žene

1000
00:43:18,240 --> 00:43:19,540
 sa djecom,

1001
00:43:19,540 --> 00:43:22,280
 onako, baš u jednu

1002
00:43:22,280 --> 00:43:23,460
 zaštitničku misiju.

1003
00:43:23,460 --> 00:43:25,460
 Dolaze, naša se djeca igraju,

1004
00:43:25,460 --> 00:43:26,460
 oni tu, kako si,

1005
00:43:26,460 --> 00:43:28,520
 ta neke obiteljske priče,

1006
00:43:29,000 --> 00:43:30,340
 a muževi dolaze do mene,

1007
00:43:30,340 --> 00:43:32,480
 a ja berujem to medaljica,

1008
00:43:32,480 --> 00:43:33,000
 križo,

1009
00:43:33,000 --> 00:43:33,700
 kao vrata sve,

1010
00:43:33,700 --> 00:43:34,620
 i one dolaze kao,

1011
00:43:34,620 --> 00:43:35,180
 e, majster,

1012
00:43:35,180 --> 00:43:36,420
 kaže, ma, pusti ovo, kaže.

1013
00:43:36,420 --> 00:43:38,420
 I mi tu krenemo pričati

1014
00:43:38,420 --> 00:43:40,620
 neke baš onako obiteljske teme.

1015
00:43:40,620 --> 00:43:42,800
 Ja tada vidim da,

1016
00:43:42,800 --> 00:43:43,840
 zapravo,

1017
00:43:43,840 --> 00:43:45,300
 ja više zajedničkoga imam

1018
00:43:45,300 --> 00:43:46,560
 sa možda jednim muslimanom

1019
00:43:46,560 --> 00:43:47,700
 koji je otvoren životu,

1020
00:43:47,700 --> 00:43:50,220
 nego sa mojim katolikom.

1021
00:43:50,220 --> 00:43:52,400
 i to je baš tužna,

1022
00:43:52,400 --> 00:43:53,880
 tužna jedna činjenica

1023
00:43:53,880 --> 00:43:55,140
 koja je mene, evo,

1024
00:43:55,140 --> 00:43:57,000
 osobno ponukala

1025
00:43:57,000 --> 00:43:58,780
 da hrabro posvjedočim.

1026
00:43:58,780 --> 00:44:02,120
 I želim i vas ohrabriti,

1027
00:44:02,120 --> 00:44:05,000
 da, evo, budemo baš onako svjetno,

1028
00:44:05,000 --> 00:44:05,740
 ne sad nešto,

1029
00:44:05,740 --> 00:44:06,960
 nije to nikakva hvala,

1030
00:44:06,960 --> 00:44:08,420
 ne jednostavno budemo hrabri

1031
00:44:08,420 --> 00:44:08,880
 oko toga,

1032
00:44:08,880 --> 00:44:11,400
 da se ne damo pokolevati,

1033
00:44:11,400 --> 00:44:12,820
 jer nije problem,

1034
00:44:12,820 --> 00:44:13,940
 nije uopće problem.

1035
00:44:13,940 --> 00:44:14,640
 Ja ne znam zašto,

1036
00:44:14,640 --> 00:44:16,400
 zašto se stavlja percepcija

1037
00:44:16,400 --> 00:44:17,100
 da je tako problem.

1038
00:44:17,100 --> 00:44:19,040
 Ja imam petera djece

1039
00:44:19,040 --> 00:44:20,320
 i spavamo uredno.

1040
00:44:20,320 --> 00:44:23,200
 Gledamo film, ja i žena.

1041
00:44:23,200 --> 00:44:24,940
 Odlazimo, šetamo se sve.

1042
00:44:24,940 --> 00:44:26,860
 Ono, danas smo u 11 sati

1043
00:44:26,860 --> 00:44:27,420
 gledali film.

1044
00:44:27,420 --> 00:44:31,460
 Ne znam, ne vidim da je to tako,

1045
00:44:31,460 --> 00:44:33,640
 ali, evo, potišemo sve skupa,

1046
00:44:33,640 --> 00:44:34,500
 evo, da budemo hrabri

1047
00:44:34,500 --> 00:44:35,120
 po tom pitanju.

1048
00:44:35,120 --> 00:44:37,420
 Ja bih vam sada ispričao nešto

1049
00:44:37,420 --> 00:44:38,040
 što je mene,

1050
00:44:38,040 --> 00:44:39,480
 što je mene i moju ženu

1051
00:44:39,480 --> 00:44:40,240
 dok smo hodali,

1052
00:44:40,240 --> 00:44:43,940
 nadahnulo da budemo otvoreni životu.

1053
00:44:43,940 --> 00:44:46,560
 Ruku na srce, evo,

1054
00:44:46,560 --> 00:44:48,220
 stvarno iskreno pričam ovdje pred vama,

1055
00:44:49,040 --> 00:44:51,260
 nisam ja planirao

1056
00:44:51,260 --> 00:44:52,700
 petera djece u šest godina,

1057
00:44:52,700 --> 00:44:53,700
 nemo se lagati,

1058
00:44:53,700 --> 00:44:54,400
 razumite.

1059
00:44:54,400 --> 00:44:55,880
 Ali evo, upravo to,

1060
00:44:55,880 --> 00:44:56,620
 otvoreni štivo,

1061
00:44:56,620 --> 00:44:57,460
 oto pa Bože moj.

1062
00:44:57,460 --> 00:44:58,500
 Ali,

1063
00:44:58,500 --> 00:45:00,420
 dok smo bili u vezi,

1064
00:45:00,420 --> 00:45:04,220
 znašli smo jednu priču

1065
00:45:04,220 --> 00:45:05,080
 iz naših korijena,

1066
00:45:07,160 --> 00:45:08,000
 janjivačka koja je nas

1067
00:45:08,000 --> 00:45:09,380
 duboko dotakla

1068
00:45:09,380 --> 00:45:11,000
 i toliko nas je ohrabrila,

1069
00:45:11,000 --> 00:45:13,320
 da smo mi baš ovo,

1070
00:45:13,320 --> 00:45:14,820
 da želimo veliku obitelji,

1071
00:45:14,820 --> 00:45:16,620
 da ćemo biti onako tu potpuno

1072
00:45:16,620 --> 00:45:17,300
 opušteni.

1073
00:45:17,300 --> 00:45:21,660
 I tako smo to odlučili u vezi,

1074
00:45:21,660 --> 00:45:22,560
 dok smo bili još,

1075
00:45:22,560 --> 00:45:23,320
 pa bih vam ja

1076
00:45:23,320 --> 00:45:24,700
 pročitao,

1077
00:45:24,700 --> 00:45:25,700
 tu sam doveo

1078
00:45:25,700 --> 00:45:26,380
 originalni

1079
00:45:26,380 --> 00:45:27,940
 novinski članak,

1080
00:45:27,940 --> 00:45:31,340
 pročitao tu jednu priču,

1081
00:45:32,160 --> 00:45:33,120
 ali prije toga ću vas

1082
00:45:33,120 --> 00:45:34,800
 uvesti u priču.

1083
00:45:34,800 --> 00:45:36,980
 Radi se o sljedećem.

1084
00:45:36,980 --> 00:45:39,080
 60-ih godina

1085
00:45:39,080 --> 00:45:41,700
 je u svijetu krenula

1086
00:45:41,700 --> 00:45:43,640
 takozvana seksualna revolucija.

1087
00:45:43,640 --> 00:45:45,680
 Hipi pokret,

1088
00:45:45,680 --> 00:45:46,440
 sve one ludosti

1089
00:45:46,440 --> 00:45:47,260
 koje se tad krenule,

1090
00:45:47,260 --> 00:45:48,740
 ono svijet ćemo preporoditi,

1091
00:45:48,740 --> 00:45:49,780
 nema grijeha,

1092
00:45:49,780 --> 00:45:50,480
 sve je dozvoljeno.

1093
00:45:50,480 --> 00:45:52,200
 Ovo što danas,

1094
00:45:52,200 --> 00:45:54,080
 ove sve ludosti postoje,

1095
00:45:54,080 --> 00:45:55,220
 to je krenulo tada.

1096
00:45:55,220 --> 00:45:57,520
 I tada,

1097
00:45:57,520 --> 00:45:58,840
 60-ih godina,

1098
00:45:58,840 --> 00:46:00,060
 na papu Pavla VI

1099
00:46:00,060 --> 00:46:01,260
 krenuli takvi napadi

1100
00:46:01,260 --> 00:46:02,880
 koje kažu

1101
00:46:02,880 --> 00:46:03,600
 tada ili tada

1102
00:46:03,600 --> 00:46:04,340
 iz svjedočanstva

1103
00:46:04,340 --> 00:46:05,340
 kardinala Šepera,

1104
